No. —.

Kosta Kisin v. State of California. On petition for a writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of the State of California in and for the County of Contra Costa. *548March 1, 1920. Per Curiam.

The motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis in this case and that the clerk of this court be directed to file the petition for a writ of certiorari herein is denied. Mr. Kosta Kisin pro se.
